public class SortedArrayDictionary<K extends java.lang.Comparable<? super K>,​V>
extends UnsortedArrayDictionary<K,​V>
implements DictionaryInterface<K,​V>
A sorted implementation of a dictionary based on arrays. NOTE: This class extends UnsortedArrayDictionary since it inherits a lot of the its methods and data fields.
